snippet.title: Pac-Man for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
#retrogaming    #PacMan #Atari #Retro #VideoGames

Get a modern Atari 2600 here! https://amzn.to/4cKQDg4

This is Pac-Man for the Atari 2600. Who in the GenX community remembers getting this for your Atari?

You can play Pac-Man for the Atari 2600 at http://2600online.com/pacman.php
Check out our alternate channel for Atari 2600 games - https://YouTube.com/2600online

Many video game historians blame this game for the Video Game Crash of 1983.
